Title: The Key to Success
Description: <A Cipher Key? Elise Starseeker might know what to do with this.>
ObjectivesText: Bring the Archaic Cipher Key to Elise Starseeker in Dornogal.
RewardText:
Astounding! This is what I've been missing. 

The map Finley found is a cipher. But this key, it's incomplete... If you find any more out there, please bring them to me. I will decipher this map, or my name isn't Elise Starseeker.
